  gcap     4x5         -      fullchem     2005070100   2005070101   -
  gcap     4x5         -      RnPbBe       2005070100   2005070101   -
  gcap     4x5         -      POPs         2005070100   2005070101   -
 !END OF RUNS:
#EOP
